探险用指令 -
  drop  get  give  go  hp  inventory  look  open  party  put
  recall  buy  sell  try 
 
状态指令 -
  score  spells  skills 

战斗用指令 -
  cast  defend  undefend  kill  remove  unwield  wear  wield  wimpy 
  consider 

沟通用指令 -
  ask  chat  tune  emote  finger  reply  say  semote  tell  who
  kingdom

王国指令 -
  kingdoms  join  rebel destroy

其他 -
  alias  help  nick  chfn  passwd  quit  save  suicide  time  to  uptime  
  hibernate  okip
详细的指令意义与用法请用 help <command> 查询。

□ 如果你是国王或大臣，请用 help king_cmds 查询专用指令。
